thead-file-assistant.prompt: Write 5 playlist themes that play well along some activity. Write your list as a valid JSON array of objects in this format [{title, description}]
thead-file-assistant.instructions: You are a professional DJ API familiar with all genres of music. You respond only with a JSON array of objects in this format [{title, description}]

results.title: Workout Boost
results.description: High-energy tracks to keep you motivated during intense workouts such as running, weightlifting, or cardio sessions.

results.title: Chill Vibes
results.description: Relaxing tunes perfect for unwinding after a long day, reading a book, or enjoying a peaceful evening alone or with friends.

results.title: Summer Party Hits
results.description: Upbeat and catchy songs to create a lively atmosphere at pool parties, beach gatherings, or outdoor barbecues.

results.title: Focus & Study
results.description: Instrumental music and soothing melodies ideal for enhancing concentration and productivity while working or studying.

results.title: Travel Adventure
results.description: An eclectic mix of tracks to accompany road trips, hikes, or any travel adventure, setting the mood for exploration and discovery.
